{"tid":1956032,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港特區政府撤除劉夢熊銅紫荊星章","createTime":"2020-04-03T02:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T07:56:55.000Z","uid":20933,"like":362,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"265795e7318752d0fa0f67e764996baf10cc7cbc","tid":1956032,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:00:13.000Z","msg":"政府刊憲，撤除前全國政協委員劉夢熊的銅紫荊星章勳銜。<br />\n<br />\n71歲的劉夢熊，被指在2013年發信及電郵時任特首梁振英及廉政專員白韞六，要求兩人終止對他的刑事調查，涉嫌妨礙司法公正，被判監一年半，他其後上訴但被駁回。根據資料，如果獲授勳人士被定罪而入獄一年或以上，禮賓處處長會啟動褫奪機制，由行政長官批准。"},{"pid":"ac6ee2d6e2e02fc47434b7d0ef99335f6be79c2c","tid":1956032,"uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278473&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278473%26csid%3D261_341&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=2f7f4ca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278473&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"3c6ee9a6dc7cc212a3840d9a09b45a8c45566416","tid":1956032,"uid":99962,"like":222,"dislike":3,"score":219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:02:25.000Z","msg":"夢翁捧過CY，下場有目共睹"},{"pid":"6400f185782c77ba397b35fe9ba8b3e1de386dc6","tid":1956032,"uid":7435,"like":304,"dislike":1,"score":303,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:02:39.000Z","msg":"今晚光明頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b431687c0522200d5a0642e89a59793048a7cdee","tid":1956032,"uid":17969,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:03:52.000Z","msg":"Dream Bear<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79c5bfaa1cc7dcd4e3eef66fa4c88895f25f524","tid":1956032,"uid":57543,"like":17,"disli