br />\n1⃣2⃣1118旺角24歲黎義士還押137日<br />\n<br />\n1⃣3⃣1118理大大屠殺26歲温義士還押130日。被逼戴裝備拍照，被圍毆，禁止看醫生<br />\n<br />\n1⃣4⃣1118油麻地23歲梅義士<br />\n<br />\n1⃣5⃣1201旺角30歲梁義士還押94日<br />\n<br />\n詳情睇被捕組🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/13579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F13579&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bg%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=a339a211\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/13579</a>"},{"pid":"eb800f876352ac7c69d0633f7ad608a6e40c5437","tid":1956032,"uid":345840,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"86b6dcc479a8ceef962e4a83d222d8255233a477","tid":1956032,"uid":289946,"like":30,"dislike":31,"score":-1,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:24:29.000Z","msg":"呢條友，做吾到行會<br />\n而家扮能晒講普世價值<br />\n最能憎呢d pk牆頭草"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:27:04.000Z","msg":"唔係牆頭草<br />\n而係接受唔到極左路線的愛國撚<br />\n好多淺藍其實都係咁"},{"pid":"d4a0c2a592a282df067f7305f79a5a0cc5a30354","tid":1956032,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b177fc64c9a37cd75b4ee29eeedaae6e5b2f8b35","tid":1956032,"uid":31237,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"b5805ca8b292922b0a4c2d3a03e9d56937bc7263","tid":1956032,"uid":42982,"like":75,"dislike":1,"score":74,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:28:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">殺人放火 大紫荊</span>"},{"pid":"7255cb251a4782f1536c691814f757ec4d88d2cf","tid":1956032,"uid":52881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:29:50.000Z","msg":"尖啤宜家都唔使要呢D虛名啦"},{"pid":"d9d993ff3fde9a2babc621641cd463528fb961d0","tid":1956032,"uid":408,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"拍錯手掌，燒錯炮仗<br />\n投錯票箱，撐